{"tid":2126311,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"深圳羅湖區通報：一名港籍貨車司機確診","createTime":"2020-07-26T18:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T01:02:31.000Z","uid":5195,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1802587f580012dcadc5aee808dbde14469d484d","tid":2126311,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"7月26日，深圳市羅湖區新冠肺炎疫情防控指揮部通告稱，26日下午，接香港衛生防護中心通報，有一名港籍貨車司機朱某康在香港被確診為新冠肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n經查，該司機按照相關<span class=\"red\">豁免</span>政策規定，於7月18日20時31分從文錦渡口岸入境，入境時核酸檢測為陰性；7月22日19時26分從文錦渡口岸返回香港，7月26日被確診為新冠肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n經流行病學調查，該司機曾在羅湖區蓮塘街道畔山花園小區本人物業逗留。為落實疫情常態化防控工作「應檢盡檢」相關要求，從即日起對該小區全體居民進行免費核酸檢測，請各位居民朋友積極配合，並加強個人日常防護措施，如有不適及時到就近發熱門診就診。"},{"pid":"9575c7b935eae06b9ffd46285aaabcb52c18a165","tid":2126311,"uid":189150,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"仆佢個街  又唔見中國人落黎播疫  有通報比香港聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6331360b1d02996e01a62e7555eda1759ef08c4d","tid":2126311,"uid":33456,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"月娥又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55fb110d8696b630683cad346eb89071ac002c8","tid":2126311,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T18:06:53.000Z","msg":"反攻大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970b734fe186a071acab6d71ecdb1b732478c812","tid